{
  "texts": [
    "For the tool-level instruction, R(S4)=1 because it \"Match\" the instruction at the tool level.",
    "Intuitively, we expect ToolPlanner to generate solutions with positive rewards.",
    "Therefore, we collected pairwise responses to further reinforce the SFT model.",
    "Specifically, we pair a negative example for each round of positive solutions.",
    "Two solution rounds can form a pairwise response if they share the same history rounds and their reward is positive and negative, respectively."
  ]
}